4/ We are moving toward a world of Autonomous Agents. But an AI agent cannot "search" a catalog like a human. It needs a structured negotiation protocol. 

O4DB is that protocol. It‚Äôs the API for the future of intent-driven commerce. 

It preserves platform control while empowering the buyer. A win-win-win for the buyer, the seller, and the ecosystem.

I just returned from a city with autonomous vehicles, yet E-commerce remains stuck in 1990s catalog logic. 
@Google @Mercadolibre 

This is a structural inefficiency.  

The problem: Burning billions in AI compute to trap "Determined Buyers" in speculative "Search -> Click" loops.  

The solution: O4DB (Only for Determined Buyer). A supplementary layer for high-intent execution.  

1. Verified Intent: Buyers broadcast a pre-validated purchase intent via @GooglePay / @mercadopago. 

2. Demand Liquidation: Sellers shift from bidding for uncertain clicks (CPC) to bidding for guaranteed acquisitions (CPA). 

3. Value-Added Bidding: Competition moves beyond price into financing, logistics, and service-level guarantees.  

For platforms, O4DB monetizes "Pure Intent" with higher margins and zero-waste compute. It bridges the gap between discovery and full agentic autonomy.  

#AI #Ecommerce #O4DB #Disruption #Fintech #AgenticEra #Waymo #FutureOfCommerce
